  "summary": "This guide will walk you through implementing serverless functions using FastAPI, a modern, fast (high-performance), web framework for building APIs with Python 3.12+.",

  "key_points": [
    "FastAPI supports asynchronous and synchronous requests out of the box",
    "FastAPI provides automatic documentation generation based on your code",
    "Integration with popular databases (PostgreSQL, SQLAlchemy, etc.) and cloud providers (AWS Lambda, Google Cloud Functions)",
